description: Discover a gem in City Point! This fully renovated penthouse condo at 804 E 6th offers stunning water views and is ready for you to move right in. With 2 bedrooms and a versatile flex room perfect for an office or nursery, this home meets all your needs. The kitchen features elegant white shaker cabinets, quartz countertops, designer lighting, stainless steel appliances, and a glass tile backsplash, all complemented by a breakfast bar that opens to a sunlit living area. Enjoy natural light streaming through bay windows with custom built-ins around the TV space. The en-suite primary bathroom includes double sinks and a spacious walk-in shower. Step out from the primary suite onto your private deck overlooking a beautifully landscaped, fenced yard. Garage parking is conveniently located next door. TWO private storage areas are included as well. Enjoy proximity to the beach, Castle Island, public transportation, and all the amenities South Boston has to offer.
